103
00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:12.879
(Cocking gun)

104
00:09:18.796 --> 00:09:23.194
- (Elliot grunting)
- (Abdullah Shafak grunting)

105
00:09:44.983 --> 00:09:47.382
(Sequins clattering)

106
00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:52.379
(Thud)

107
00:09:55.658 --> 00:09:58.176
